Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The morning we were born, we were handed a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}rather unfair travelling bag that we've carried with us to this place of learning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Quick to envy, looking down on others at times
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cowardly selves clashing as our shining luggage kept increasing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All too many things have happened; we simply repeat the words we could never say right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, just the words "I'm sorry" and "Thank you," over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Our memories will be our source of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding tightly onto the dreams we had found individually
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On a path so long we could never hope to reach the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we will simply continue to walk on resolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friends. We may be parting today..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friends. But this pain within..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friends. Proves the depth of our love."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friends. Don't forget."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)}"Friends. Our radiant..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}The last bell breaks through the air and resounds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shoulders trembled ever so faintly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We close our eyes just once more, and say with a deep breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, "Farewell" and "Thank you" for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When they broke, we picked up the pieces and put them back together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we regain our grip our slightly chipped dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as we find ourselves in doubt or as we cry, we will never stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,aiming for the brightest future, starting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How many billion light years of solitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we may always be apart, if you look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bottom of these skies, we've still clung on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, even if there is nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)}we softly vow in our chests to take flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)}Our memories will be our source of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding tightly onto the dreams we had found individually
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,On a path so long we could never hope to reach the end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)}Even so, we will simply continue to walk on resolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}The wind still blows cold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}But we will keep our heads up
